# InputGroup — Style Spec

## CSS Classes

| Class | Element | Notes |
|-------|---------|-------|
| `.acko-input-group` | Root wrapper | `flex row`, border, rounded-full |
| `.acko-input-group-sm` | Small size | Height: var(--space-9) |
| `.acko-input-group-md` | Medium size | Height: var(--scale-44) |
| `.acko-input-group-lg` | Large size | Height: var(--scale-52) |
| `.acko-input-group-prefix` | Left addon | `padding: 0 --space-3`, border-right separator |
| `.acko-input-group-suffix` | Right addon | `padding: 0 --space-3`, border-left separator |
| `.acko-input-group-input` | Inner input | `flex: 1`, transparent bg |
| `.acko-input-group-error` | Error state | `border-color: --color-error` |
| `.acko-input-group-disabled` | Disabled state | `opacity: 0.5`, `pointer-events: none` |

## Token Usage
- Border: `--color-input-border`
- Background: `--color-input-bg`
- Focus: `--color-primary` border, `--color-primary-ring` shadow
- Error: `--color-error`
- Addon text: `--color-text-muted`
- Input text: `--color-text-default`
